  <div class="comment_head"><a href="/user/redbell">redbell</a> 2 days ago</div>
  <div class="comment_text">This behavior of blocking some domains and IP ranges during LaLiga games has become a routine by now. You might also want to check these similar submissions:<p>My game&#x27;s server is blocked in Spain whenever there&#x27;s a football match on: <a href="https:&#x2F;&#x2F;news.ycombinator.com&#x2F;item?id=45358433">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;news.ycombinator.com&#x2F;item?id=45358433</a><p>Spain’s LaLiga has blocked access to freedom.gov: <a href="https:&#x2F;&#x2F;news.ycombinator.com&#x2F;item?id=47114235">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;news.ycombinator.com&#x2F;item?id=47114235</a></div>
